Prominent politicians such as Deputy President William Ruto and ODM party leader Raila Odinga set a bad example continuing their mobilisation around the 2022 presidential succession race and the Building Bridges Initiative (BBI) reforms. Not quite surprisingly, that list of shame included President Uhuru Kenyatta who had himself imposed the restrictions!
Police brutality won’t go away



